@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((v1 + (v1 + 0.70 + v1 + 0.74)) - 0.63)
    tmp = wp.sin(0.31)
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.abs(wp.cos(v2 + 0.90)))
    v1 = wp.abs(0.39)
    tmp = 0.79
    v2 = (0.11 - v2)
    v2 = ((v1 * (tmp + 0.87 / v0 + 0.98)) / wp.abs(v0))
    data[tid] = v0
